w.metabase.com/changelog/56#metabase-565"]},{"version":"v0.56.4","released":"2025-09-02","patch":true,"highlights":["ci(sdk): version bump for Next.js for host apps e2e tests","Add Jeff's suggestions from #62929","Auto-update documentation for release-x.56.x","Add Snowflake JDBC error troubleshooting section","don't document metabot env vars","docs(sdk): Update SDK version to 0.56.3","ci(sdk): Update release-embedding-sdk.yml workflow file to set proper `lastest` tag","[Search] Fix schema version number for search snowplow event","Update timezone troubleshooting guide","Pivot raw totals export is blank on Oracle DB","typo in embedding js docs","Fix the default value for `case-sensitive` for string filter clauses","Migrate to cloud  on 56 doesn't redirect to store but to localhost","Visualizer combination gets messed up when Adding series (cannot find a pattern why)","ci: use openldap from legacy registry","Hide CSV panel with no meaningful uploadable dbs","Fix for code scanning alert no. 512: Insecure randomness","Fix deselecting fields in joins with inactive implicitly joined remapped columns","docs - relative links","docs - fix markdown links in Debian installation guide","feat(sdk): Fix and improve Metabot for SDK","Fix: UXW-204 don't show upsells to non-admins on paid plans","update jspdf to 3.0.2","Auto-update documentation for release-x.56.x","Navigating Settings Presents Error When you Select Auth or Embedding Sections","docs - note on pinning","Add documentation for password settings on Metabase Cloud","docs - clarify JWT Identity Provider URI instructions","Manual backport of preserving table whitespaces changes","Postgres queries fail with `java.lang.Class.isArray()` errors after upgrade to v0.56.3","A caret cursor is not visible in filter inputs","Content layout shift when checking an item in a collection","Pivot table export outputs blank values when pivoting on integer columns","Auto-update documentation for release-x.56.x","Better branch detection if relevant files are changed for CI","Fix flaky UpdatesNavItem test","Update Debian/systemd docs","Fix references to pre-56 Troubleshooting admin menu","Drill through no longer works for pivot tables in the latest version","Fix flaky test for metabase-browser custom element","Card filters seem to be avoiding the linkage to dashboard filters","Discard cached field values will... refresh the values?","Fix tabs alignment for horizontal tabs with grow (#61895)","docs: translations limitations","skip flaky loki row chart tests","There are more selected columns than there are total columns","refactor(sdk): Rename embedding-sdk directory to embedding-sdk-bundle","chore: upgrade vulnerable cipher-base package","chore: upgrade vulnerable sha.js package","[BOT-316] Metabase BE support for dynamic agent profiles","Respond with HTTP status 500 when Store API request fails during Cloud migration","fix(sdk): Add background-light to derived colors for the new embed","Content Translation doesn't translate pivot table columns","publicly-shared dashboards show blank pages when viewed in incognito (or by non-authenticated users)","[Metabot] Add `available_actions` to metabot context","Download button overlaps table header with embedding title is not enabled.","Cannot assign certain column types to fields in models","[QP] Don't apply `:coercion-strategy` to joined fields twice","feat(embed js flow): use widget for initial parameters","Fix invitation not being sent from /setup flow","Data picker skeleton is vertically shifted","[Search] Increase search reporting","Content translation copy uses wrong header name","[METABOT] Do not apply update-keys to ai-service request state","Cast to a Datetime doesn't play well with Joins on the Query Editor","Labels on inputs in the new-dashboard modal are incorrectly using font-weight: 800","dashboardId must be an int - error displayed for embedded maps with more than 1000 pins","bump arrow to 17 for parquet issue","Edit visualization on visualizer car